        h4.privacy-form__subtitle ABOUT YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION
        p.privacy-form__text The information you provide here will be processed solely for the purpose of verifying your identity and residency, identifying the information you're requesting, and answering your request. Your data (including the data associated with this form) will be removed once your request has been answered.
        h4.privacy-form__subtitle HOW WE WILL PROCESS YOUR REQUEST
        p.privacy-form__text We will answer your request, or request additional information from you within 30 days. We may extend this process for up to two months, in which case we will notify you of the extension within a month. The processing of this request is free of charge, but we reserve the right, as allowed under applicable law, to charge an administrative fee under certain circumstances.
        p.privacy-form__text If you would prefer to submit your request via email, please email us at: <a href="#">privacy@ebsi.com</a>

